			<visible>Skin.HasSetting(Use_Fanart_Viz) + ![Skin.HasSetting(vis_photos_backdrops) | Skin.HasSetting(vis_music_backdrops)] + !Skin.HasSetting(Artist_Slideshow)</visible>
